This form is intended to fully acknowledge and apologize for the incident summarized above. The NFSD takes full responsibility for any damages and inconveniences from the incident, and the offending officer(s) supervisor(s) have handled matters internally. The NFSD is available if you wish to seek a settlement to cover the damages you incurred. You are also entitled to seek a civil lawsuit if a settlement agreeable to both sides can not be made. 

We, the New Frontier Sheriff Department, are sincerely sorry for the events of the incident.

